object.customQuery:
WITH current_batch AS (
    SELECT 
        bls.batch_id,
        bls.source_start_cutoff_datetime,
        bls.source_end_cutoff_datetime
    FROM $$operational_schema.batch_load_summary bls
    WHERE bls.source_system_code = '$$sourcesystemcode'
      AND bls.batch_status = 'Inprogress'
      AND bls.target_schema_name = '$$refined_schema'
      AND bls.batch_id = (
          SELECT MAX(batch_id)
          FROM $$operational_schema.batch_load_summary
          WHERE source_system_code = '$$sourcesystemcode'
            AND batch_status = 'Inprogress'
            AND target_schema_name = '$$refined_schema'
      )
),
address_data AS (
SELECT DISTINCT 
    NULL AS address_id,
    'ADM' AS address_source_system,
    'Agency' AS address_domain,
    CASE
        WHEN ag.type = 'C' THEN 'Commissions Address'
        WHEN ag.type = 'M' THEN 'Mailing Address'
        ELSE NULL
    END AS address_type,
    NULL AS address_batch_id,
    ISNULL(ag.originating_source_name, NULL) AS originating_source_name,
    ISNULL(ag.originating_load_type, NULL) AS originating_load_type,
    GETDATE() AS address_row_effective_start_datetime,
    '9999-12-31 00:00:00.000000'::timestamp AS address_row_effective_end_datetime,
    ag.adm_address_guidewire_row_status AS address_row_status,
    NULL AS address_row_md5checksum,
    'prd_informatica' AS address_row_created_by, --**Note:Review 
    'prd_informatica' AS address_row_modified_by, --**Note:Review 
    'Loaded' AS address_row_load_state,
    ISNULL(ag.id, NULL) AS address_row_source_system_key,
    '1 - Primary' AS address_rank,
    ISNULL(UPPER(ag.address1), NULL) AS address_line1,
    ISNULL(UPPER(ag.address2), NULL) AS address_line2,
    NULL AS address_line3,
    NULL AS address_line4,
    CASE
        WHEN ag.address1 IS NULL AND ag.address2 IS NULL THEN NULL
        WHEN ag.address1 IS NOT NULL AND ag.address2 IS NOT NULL
            THEN UPPER(ag.address1) || ', ' || UPPER(ag.address2)
        WHEN ag.address1 IS NOT NULL
            THEN UPPER(ag.address1)
        WHEN ag.address2 IS NOT NULL
            THEN UPPER(ag.address2)
        ELSE NULL
    END AS address_lines_consolidated,
    ISNULL(UPPER(ag.city), NULL) AS address_city_name,
    CASE
        WHEN TRIM(ag.state) IS NULL OR TRIM(ag.state) = '' THEN NULL
        WHEN us.usa_state_and_territory_alpha_2_code IS NOT NULL
            THEN us.usa_state_and_territory_alpha_2_code
        ELSE NULL
    END AS address_usa_state_and_territory_alpha_2_code,
    ISNULL(ag.zip, NULL) AS address_postal_code,
    CASE
        WHEN TRIM(ag.country) IS NULL OR TRIM(ag.country) = '' THEN NULL
        WHEN LENGTH(TRIM(ag.country)) = 2
             AND wc.country_iso_alpha_2_code IS NOT NULL
            THEN wc.country_iso_alpha_3_code
        WHEN LENGTH(TRIM(ag.country)) = 3
             AND wc.country_iso_alpha_3_code IS NOT NULL
            THEN wc.country_iso_alpha_3_code
        ELSE NULL
    END AS address_country_iso_alpha_3_code,
    ISNULL(ag.created, '1900-01-01 00:00:00') AS address_row_source_system_created_datetime,
    ISNULL(ag.modified, '1900-01-01 00:00:00') AS address_row_source_system_modified_datetime
FROM $$staging_schema.adm_address_guidewire ag
LEFT JOIN $$reference_schema.usa_states_and_territories us
    ON UPPER(TRIM(ag.state)) = us.usa_state_and_territory_alpha_2_code
	AND ag.adm_address_guidewire_row_effective_end_datetime = '9999-12-31 00:00:00.000000'
	AND us.usa_state_and_territory_row_effective_end_datetime = '9999-12-31 00:00:00.000000'
LEFT JOIN $$reference_schema.world_countries wc
    ON UPPER(TRIM(ag.country)) IN (
        wc.country_iso_alpha_2_code,
        wc.country_iso_alpha_3_code
    )
	AND wc.world_country_row_effective_end_datetime = '9999-12-31 00:00:00.000000'

UNION

SELECT DISTINCT NULL AS address_id,
       'ADM' AS address_source_system,
       'Agency' AS address_domain,
       'Physical Location' AS address_type, -- ETL Generated
 NULL AS address_batch_id,
 ISNULL($$staging_schema.adm_t_agency.originating_source_name, NULL) AS originating_source_name,
 ISNULL($$staging_schema.adm_t_agency.originating_load_type, NULL) AS originating_load_type,
 GETDATE() AS address_row_effective_start_datetime,
 '9999-12-31 00:00:00.000000'::timestamp AS address_row_effective_end_datetime,
 $$staging_schema.adm_t_agency.adm_t_agency_row_status AS address_row_status, -- ETL Generated
 NULL AS address_row_md5checksum,
 'prd_informatica' AS address_row_created_by, --**Note:Review
 'prd_informatica' AS address_row_modified_by, --**Note:Review
 'Loaded' AS address_row_load_state,
 ISNULL($$staging_schema.adm_t_agency.agency_nup, NULL) AS address_row_source_system_key,
 CASE
     WHEN $$staging_schema.adm_t_agency.location_num IS NOT NULL THEN $$staging_schema.adm_t_agency.location_num || ' - Primary'
     ELSE NULL
 END AS address_rank,
 ISNULL(UPPER($$staging_schema.adm_t_agency.agency_str_1), NULL) AS address_line1,
 ISNULL(UPPER($$staging_schema.adm_t_agency.agency_str_2), NULL) AS address_line2,
 ISNULL(UPPER($$staging_schema.adm_t_agency.agency_str_3), NULL) AS address_line3,
 NULL AS address_line4, -- Consolidated address lines
 NULLIF(TRIM(BOTH ', '
             FROM COALESCE(NULLIF(UPPER($$staging_schema.adm_t_agency.agency_str_1), NULL) || ', ', '') || COALESCE(NULLIF(UPPER($$staging_schema.adm_t_agency.agency_str_2), NULL) || ', ', '') || COALESCE(NULLIF(UPPER($$staging_schema.adm_t_agency.agency_str_3), NULL), '')), '') AS address_lines_consolidated,
 ISNULL(UPPER($$staging_schema.adm_t_agency.agency_city), NULL) AS address_city_name,
 CASE
     WHEN TRIM($$staging_schema.adm_t_agency.agency_st) IS NULL
          OR TRIM($$staging_schema.adm_t_agency.agency_st) = '' THEN NULL
     WHEN us.usa_state_and_territory_alpha_2_code IS NOT NULL THEN us.usa_state_and_territory_alpha_2_code
     ELSE NULL
 END AS address_usa_state_and_territory_alpha_2_code,
 ISNULL($$staging_schema.adm_t_agency.agency_zip, NULL) AS address_postal_code,
 NULL AS address_country_iso_alpha_3_code,
 ISNULL($$staging_schema.adm_t_agency.create_date, '1900-01-01 00:00:00') AS address_row_source_system_created_datetime,
 ISNULL($$staging_schema.adm_t_agency.last_modified, '1900-01-01 00:00:00') AS address_row_source_system_modified_datetime
FROM $$staging_schema.adm_t_agency
LEFT JOIN $$reference_schema.usa_states_and_territories us
    ON UPPER(TRIM($$staging_schema.adm_t_agency.agency_st)) = us.usa_state_and_territory_alpha_2_code
    AND adm_t_agency.adm_t_agency_row_effective_end_datetime = '9999-12-31 00:00:00.000000'
	AND us.usa_state_and_territory_row_effective_end_datetime = '9999-12-31 00:00:00.000000'
)
SELECT DISTINCT 
ad.address_id,
ad.address_source_system,
ad.address_domain,
ad.address_type,
cb.batch_id as address_batch_id,
ad.originating_source_name,
ad.originating_load_type,
ad.address_row_effective_start_datetime,
ad.address_row_effective_end_datetime,
ad.address_row_status,
MD5(
    COALESCE(ad.address_row_status, '') || '|' ||
    COALESCE(ad.address_lines_consolidated, '') || '|' ||
    COALESCE(ad.address_city_name, '') || '|' ||
    COALESCE(ad.address_usa_state_and_territory_alpha_2_code, '') || '|' ||
    COALESCE(ad.address_postal_code, '') || '|' ||
    COALESCE(ad.address_country_iso_alpha_3_code, '') || '|' ||
	COALESCE(ad.address_type, '')
) AS address_row_md5checksum,

ad.address_row_created_by,
ad.address_row_modified_by,
ad.address_row_load_state,
ad.address_row_source_system_key,
ad.address_rank,
ad.address_line1,
ad.address_line2,
ad.address_line3,
ad.address_line4,
ad.address_lines_consolidated,
ad.address_city_name,
ad.address_usa_state_and_territory_alpha_2_code,
ad.address_postal_code,
ad.address_country_iso_alpha_3_code,
ad.address_row_source_system_created_datetime,
ad.address_row_source_system_modified_datetime,
tgt.originating_source_name as tgt_originating_source_name,
tgt.address_type as tgt_address_type,
tgt.address_row_source_system_key as tgt_address_row_source_system_key,
tgt.address_row_md5checksum as tgt_address_row_md5checksum,
tgt.address_id as tgt_address_id

FROM address_data ad
left join 
	(select originating_source_name,
	address_type,
	address_row_source_system_key,
	address_row_md5checksum,
	address_id
	from silver.addresses
	where address_row_effective_end_datetime= '9999-12-31 00:00:00.000000' 
	) tgt
on ad.originating_source_name = tgt.originating_source_name
and ad.address_type = tgt.address_type
and ad.address_row_source_system_key = tgt.address_row_source_system_key
left join current_batch cb on true
where ad.address_row_source_system_key = 2009
